CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1771956278
OL,3,CTributes for 'tenacious campaigner'
OL,4,Cwho set up leading HIV charity
OL,6,FThe charity started with humble
OL,7,Fbeginnings, with Mr Butler using his
OL,8,Fown home phone number for the first
OL,9,FAids helpline.
OL,11,FHe supported the charity for five
OL,12,Fdecades and was made an OBE for
OL,13,Fservices to charity and public health.
OL,15,FMr Butler was born in Newport, Wales,
OL,16,Fand moved to London in the 1970s,
OL,17,Fwhere he worked in advertising, cinema
OL,18,Fand entertainment.
OL,20,FHe met Terry Higgins and the pair
OL,21,Fworked together at Heaven nightclub.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1771956278
OL,3,CTributes for 'tenacious campaigner'
OL,4,Cwho set up leading HIV charity
OL,6,FMr Butler's death was announced on
OL,7,FMonday (February 23).
OL,9,FHis brother Guy Hewett said: "We are
OL,10,Fheartbroken to lose him so suddenly
OL,11,Fbut full of pride for all he achieved.
OL,13,F"He saw it as a duty to inform the
OL,14,Fcountry, and in particular the gay
OL,15,Fcommunity, of what little information
OL,16,Fthere was on HIV and Aids in the early
OL,17,F1980s.
OL,19,F"He took great joy in seeing what
OL,20,FTerrence Higgins Trust has become and
OL,21,Fstayed involved to the very end.
OL,26,@qD@^OUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1771956278
OL,3,CTributes for 'tenacious campaigner'
OL,4,Cwho set up leading HIV charity
OL,6,F"Grief is the terrible price of love,
OL,7,Fbut we know his legacy lives on."
OL,9,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,10,F"Martyn Butler was a tenacious
OL,11,Fcampaigner for people living with HIV.
OL,13,F"He had both the foresight to set up
OL,14,FTerrence Higgins Trust and the insight
OL,15,Fto name it after his friend to
OL,16,Fhumanise the Aids epidemic, which has
OL,17,Fshaped the UK's response to HIV.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@aO]rD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1771956278
OL,3,CTributes for 'tenacious campaigner'
OL,4,Cwho set up leading HIV charity
OL,6,F"As Health Secretary, it was my
OL,7,Fprivilege to be part of his fifth
OL,8,Fdecade of championing HIV prevention,
OL,9,Fsupport and remembrance.
OL,11,F"We are all forever in his debt and
OL,12,Fhis legacy lives on."
OL,14,FGareth Thomas, former British Lions
OL,15,Frugby captain and Terrence Higgins
OL,16,FTrust patron, said: "Martyn Butler
OL,17,Ffounding Terrence Higgins Trust
OL,18,Fbrought a distinctly Welsh feel to
OL,19,Feverything done by the organisation
OL,20,Fdedicated to a fellow Welshman.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@UO]xD@UOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1771956278
OL,3,CTributes for 'tenacious campaigner'
OL,4,Cwho set up leading HIV charity
OL,6,F"He was a trailblazer that stuck at
OL,7,Fthe cause of supporting people living
OL,8,Fwith HIV over five decades.
OL,10,F"I will not forget his smile and we
OL,11,Fcontinue the fight in his memory."
OL,13,FRichard Angell, Terrence Higgins Trust
OL,14,Fchief executive, said the announcement
OL,15,Fhad come as a "shock", adding:
OL,16,F"Terrence Higgins Trust literally
OL,17,Fwouldn't be here if it wasn't for
OL,18,FMartyn.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@bO]wD@OOUwD@UO]xD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
