OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1771956278
OL,3,CTributes for 'tenacious campaigner'
OL,4,Cwho set up leading HIV charity
OL,6,F"When it came to the organisation and
OL,7,Fpeople living with HIV, nothing was
OL,8,Ftoo much trouble for him.
OL,10,F"From our first fundraiser, speaking
OL,11,Fengagement, and leaflet to marching at
OL,12,FCardiff Pride, unveiling Terry
OL,13,FHiggins' blue plaque in Haverfordwest
OL,14,Fand talking to media, Martyn has
OL,15,Fwalked with us every step of the way.
OL,17,F"He was determined, spirited and never
OL,18,Ftook no for an answer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
