OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1771956278
OL,3,CTributes for 'tenacious campaigner'
OL,4,Cwho set up leading HIV charity
OL,6,F"Kind to a fault, he was also brave `
OL,7,Fgiving his home phone number as the
OL,8,Ffirst Aids helpline in 1983 ` and
OL,9,Fcaring, and an inspiration to other
OL,10,Fdeaf people everywhere.
OL,12,F"He will be missed by the Terrence
OL,13,FHiggins Trust family, his mother,
OL,14,Fsiblings and the friends so lucky to
OL,15,Fspend time with him."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@UO]
